 Aelfric, and Wulfstan, among others.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aAnglo-SaxonsvLiterary collections. 0aAnglo-SaxonsxLiterary collections. 0aEnglish literaturexModernized versionsxOld English, ca. 450-1100. 0aEnglish literatureyOld English, ca. 450-1100vModernized versions. 0aMiddle AgesvLiterary collections. 0aMiddle AgesxLiterary collections. 7aPOETRY / General.2bisacsh1 aOlsen, Alexandra H., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aRaffel, Burton.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311053799440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030013041640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300130416423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300130416/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles